        "collapsible_tab_YdNQfV": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "DESCRIPTION",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>CozyPod™ — Small Space Heat. Engineered to Perform.</p><p>Meet CozyPod, the world’s most powerful plug-in heater designed for compact spaces up to 300 sq ft. Whether you’re warming a bedroom, RV, office, or workspace, CozyPod delivers fast, efficient heat exactly where you need it.</p><p><br/>At its core is a 1500W PTC ceramic heating system that reaches full warmth in just 2 seconds, providing powerful, consistent heat without exposed elements. The integrated remote control stores in the base and self-charges — no batteries ever required, so control is always within reach.</p><p><br/>Eco Mode lets you maintain your ideal room temperature efficiently, while the built-in timer allows you to set exactly how long CozyPod runs — delivering comfort with intelligent energy control.</p><p><br/>Built for safety and reliability, CozyPod features a fire-retardant shell, is safety tested for the U.S. market. Important: CozyPod is designed for use with standard U.S. 3-prong outlets (120V) and is intended for U.S. homes only.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_M7w3tC": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "SPECS",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p><strong>Heating Coverage: </strong>Up to 300 Sq Feet</p><p><strong>Dimensions:</strong> 7.5in x 5.2in x 4.5in</p><p><strong>Watts</strong>: 800/1200/1500</p><p><strong>Amps: </strong>15</p><p><strong>Decibels: </strong>40</p><p><strong>Motor: </strong>3600 RPM</p><p><strong>Temp Range: </strong>60-90F</p><p><strong>Material: </strong>Flame Retardant PC</p><p><strong>Safety Standard:</strong> UL1278</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_ncARP4": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
